ChatGPT said:

Shum mir po e mendon!
Kjo sht mnyra profesionale: punon n nj branch t ri, e teston, pastaj e bashkon me main.

Ja si me kriju dhe me punu me branch t ri:

1. Krijo nj branch t ri

N terminal:

nginx
git branch emri-branchit

p.sh.:

nginx
git branch design

2. Kalo n branch-in e ri

nginx
git checkout design

ose me nj komand t shpejt (krijon + kalon):

css
git checkout -b design

3. Bj ndryshimet n kt branch

Tash do file q ndryshon sht vetm n design, jo n main.

4. Shto dhe commit

sql
git add .
git commit -m "Ndryshime n dizajn"

5. Pusho branch-in t ri n GitHub

Hern e par duhet me vendos upstream:

cpp
git push --set-upstream origin design

Pastaj vetm:

perl
git push

6. Kur t jesh gati me e bashku me main

Shkon n GitHub Pull Request Merge.

OSE lokalisht:

css
git checkout main
git merge design
git push

Nse do, t tregoj edhe si me fshi branch, me pa cilat ekzistojn, ose me punu me disa njkohsisht vetm thuaj!

4) products.js

JavaScript q i lexon t dhnat prej URL dhe i shfaq produktet

js
// Lista e produkteve
const products = {
    lipstick1: {
        name: "Red Matte Lipstick",
        price: "12.99",
        image: "images/lipstick1.png",
        description: "Long-lasting red matte lipstick. Perfect for Christmas looks."
    },
    eyebrow1: {
        name: "Natural Eyebrow Pencil",
        price: "9.99",
        image: "images/eyebrow1.png",
        description: "Soft, natural eyebrow pencil with longwear formula."
    },
    brush1: {
        name: "Mini Brush Set",
        price: "14.99",
        image: "images/brush1.png",
        description: "High-quality mini brush set ideal for light & glam makeup."
    }
};

// Merr ID e produktit nga URL
const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
const productId = params.get("id");

// Gjej produktin
const product = products[productId];

// Vendos t dhnat n HTML
if (product) {
    document.getElementById("product-name").textContent = product.name;
    document.getElementById("product-price").textContent = product.price;
    document.getElementById("product-desc").textContent = product.description;
    document.getElementById("product-image").src = product.image;
}
